name: Ryan's Mystery Playdate: Level Up
overview: Ryan's Mystery Playdate follows Ryan, his parents and animated friends Gus the Gummy Gator and Combo Panda as they work together to tackle a series of imaginative, physical challenges and unbox puzzles to reveal the identity of his mystery playdate.
